"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-09-09-Olympic-athletes-call-for-fair-treatment-and-not-politicizing-sports-1wLcTWncAJW-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  In the Olympics Champions Special Program, CGTN brings together several athletes from the Paris Olympics in an AR virtual studio to discuss their experiences and reflections on the Games.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"/CGTN  As the 2024 Paris Olympic and Paralympic Games officially concluded, CGTN talked to several Chinese athletes, who shared their stories and experiences on the Games.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9090485694773118, \"rank\": 0.09649993397713415, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chinese boxer Li Qian recalled a touching moment when she hugged her opponent, Atheyna Bylon of Panama, after the final.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 580, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9090485694773118, \"rank\": 0.09649993397713415, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atheyna_Bylon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Atheyna Bylon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atheyna_Bylon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atheyna_Bylon\"}, {\"begin\": 676, \"end\": 682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panama\", \"score\": 0.9999999996011866, \"rank\": 2.0322582368232695e-10, \"text\": \"Panama\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panama\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a mutual appreciation between athletes.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because we understand each other better, we know how hard it's been to get here,\\\" Li reflected.\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 833, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"score\": 0.9934697659029155, \"rank\": 0.0065731583594314915, \"text\": \"Li\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For some other athletes, such moments, embodying the spirit of sportsmanship and the Olympics, are exactly what they have not experienced but wish to call for.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 1007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though the Chinese swimming team had undergone the largest number of doping tests before and during the Paris Games, with every member fully tested, Chinese athletes faced suspicion and skepticism.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1025, \"end\": 1032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9090485694773118, \"rank\": 0.09649993397713415, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1163, \"end\": 1170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9090485694773118, \"rank\": 0.09649993397713415, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swimmer Zhang Yufei, who topped the list of medals won by a swimmer in Paris with haul of 6 medals, admitted that unfriendly voices and unfair treatment embroiled the team in Paris.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1220, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yufei_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9727864122994488, \"rank\": 0.027972027972030022, \"text\": \"Zhang Yufei\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yufei_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yufei_(swimmer)\"}, {\"begin\": 1283, \"end\": 1288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996860038247, \"rank\": 3.139962845009379e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1387, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996860038247, \"rank\": 3.139962845009379e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang recalled receiving some \\\"unfriendly attitudes\\\" at times during the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old gave a fiery response to the doping allegations surrounding the Chinese swimming team.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1561, \"end\": 1568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9090485694773118, \"rank\": 0.09649993397713415, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the past decade, China has made unprecedented efforts to become a leading global sports power and to provide its athletes with world-class support and facilities, which Zhang emphasized during the discussion.\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999874025254439, \"rank\": 8.850689301325731e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whether it's our training facilities, diet, accommodations, or even our overseas training, we are ensured to have access to the best equipment,\\\" said Zhang.\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1957, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is with such support and the legacy of the Olympic spirit that the Chinese delegation has achieved remarkable results and made continuous breakthroughs in Paris.\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2029, \"end\": 2036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9090485694773118, \"rank\": 0.09649993397713415, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2117, \"end\": 2122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996860038247, \"rank\": 3.139962845009379e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Notably, China claimed its first-ever gold medal in artistic swimming at Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2133, \"end\": 2138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999874025254439, \"rank\": 8.850689301325731e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Artistic swimmer Feng Yu expressed her immense joy and gratitude, noting that her generation of athletes is \\\"fortunate\\\".\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2226, \"end\": 2233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Feng_Yu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Feng Yu\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Feng_Yu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Feng_Yu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She attributed their opportunities to the enduring spirit, perseverance, and legacy of those who came before, which has allowed them to build on past successes and pursue their own dreams.\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2780, \"entities\": []}]}"